Package: PsyMetricTools
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Psychometric and Statistical Analysis Tools
Description: A comprehensive package designed for psychometric and statistical
    analysis in social sciences. It includes functions for data preprocessing,
    factor analysis, reliability testing, descriptive statistics, visualization
    of Likert-scale items, measurement invariance analysis, and handling
    multi-class imbalances. The package facilitates advanced data analysis
    tasks commonly encountered in psychological and educational research.
    Includes an updated easy_invariance() function for ordinal data following
    Wu and Estabrook (2016) <doi:10.1037/met0000051>.
